2. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the complexity of the proposed algorithm and compares it to other decoding algorithms, which is a topic related to computational complexity. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper mentions data flow and communication between nodes, which are topics related to social and information networks. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new decoding algorithm for product codes, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the data flow and communication between nodes in the decoding algorithm, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture.
